%section#Services.section.mcb-section
  .column.mcb-column.one.column_divider
    %hr.no_line{:style => "margin: 0 auto 80px"}/
  .section_wrapper.mcb-section-inner
    .title-section
      %h4.themecolor{:style => "margin-bottom: 6px"} Our services
      %h2 know more about our services
    .content-services
      %a.content-services_item{:href=>"services.html"}
        .content-services_img.content-img
          %img{:src => "https://www.torqueayurveda.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/eab1f3_d8d9559b21ff48c2b2b72923408d20fc_mv2.jpg"}/
        .content-services__content.content-column-services{"data-anim-type" => "fadeInUp", :style => "background-color:rgba(239, 66, 111, 0.26);"}
          .content-services__title
            %h5{:style => "text-align: center"}
              Energetic alignment of physical, mental, emotional and spiritual body
          .content-services_line
            %div{:style => "width: 80px; height: 5px; background: #ef426f; border-radius: 3px; margin: 0 auto"}
            %hr.no_line{:style => "margin: 0 auto 15px"}/
          %p.content-services_description{:style =>"font-weight: 300;font-family: 'Roboto';font-size: 15px;"}
            A holistic therapy that understands the individual as a Whole (mind-emotion-body-spirit) and that proposes to align our life with the purest part of our Being, our true essence.
      %a.content-services_item{:href=>"services.html"}
        .content-services_img.content-img
          %img{:src => "assets/img/limpieza.jpg"}/
        .content-services__content.content-column-services{"data-anim-type" => "fadeInUp", :style => "background-color: rgba(89, 49, 95, 0.12);"}
          .content-services__title
            %h5{:style => "text-align: center"}
              Cleaning the spinal column
          .content-services_line
            %div{:style => "width: 80px; height: 5px; background: #59315f; border-radius: 3px; margin: 0 auto"}
            %hr.no_line{:style => "margin: 0 auto 15px"}/
          %p.description-services{:style =>"font-weight: 300;font-family: 'Roboto';font-size: 15px;"}
            A fundamental habit for self-healing is to maintain an active energy system by cleansing and flexibilizing the spine. Our spine supports not only our body, but is the physical counterpart of the most important energy channels (nadhis) of our system.
      %a.content-services_item{:href=>"services.html"}
        .content-services_img.content-img
          %img{:src => "assets/img/manos2.webp"}/
        .content-services__content.content-column-services{"data-anim-type" => "fadeInUp", :style => "background-color:rgba(248, 163, 188, 0.23);"} 
          .content-services__title
            %h5{:style => "text-align: center"} 
              Ancestral Lineage
          .content-services_line
            %div{:style => "width: 80px; height: 5px; background: #f48fb1; border-radius: 3px; margin: 0 auto"}
            %hr.no_line{:style => "margin: 0 auto 15px"}/
          %p.content-services_description{:style =>"font-weight: 300;font-family: 'Roboto';font-size: 15px;"}
            One of the most important tasks we have in this existence is to identify and release the patterns, behaviors and beliefs that we have inherited from our maternal and paternal lineage. These inherited patterns distort our outlook on life. 

